messages.message: :tada: UI update - Bookmarks have been revamped! :tada: Unlike before, only file system paths (and not app URLs) can be bookmarked. You can now bookmark and un-bookmark any path in File Explorer, the File Picker, and any app with breadcrumbs. The bookmarks manager is still located in the File Explorer and can be opened from the top bar. Try it out and give us feedback atÂ <#CLBGA5A7K|>!
